"Shell-ip naammassineqarnera Bash-versioninut 4.4-mit utoqqaanerusunut "
"tapersersorneqanngilaq."

msgid "Couldn't detect Bash version, shell completion is not supported."
msgstr ""
"Bash-version nassaarisinnaanngilara, shell-ip naammassineqarnera "
"tapersersorneqanngilaq."

